    "# SupplyChainOptix - Exploratory Data Analysis & Model Prototyping\n",
    "\n",
    "**Purpose**: Initial exploration of supply chain data sources, anomaly detection testing, and forecasting model prototypes.\n",
    "\n",
    "**Data Sources**:\n",
    "- Shipment records (delivery times, routes, carrier performance)\n",
    "- Inventory levels (warehouse stock, SKU turnover)\n",
    "- Geopolitical events (scraped news, API feeds)\n",
    "- Weather data (port conditions, transport disruptions)\n",
    "\n",
    "**Models to Prototype**:\n",
    "1. Isolation Forest for anomaly detection\n",
    "2. Prophet for time series forecasting\n",
    "3. Random Forest for delay classification\n",
    "\n",
    "**Author**: Supply Chain Analytics Team  \n",
    "**Last Updated**: 2024-01"
